lines.text: [Toby rights something on a note and gives it to Garret]
Somebody needs to get raped here. You perversed fucker.
Right so I can read it
[Flipping Garret off, writes a new note and gives it to Garret]

[to the camera]
You know I really don't think I like camping that much.
The funny thing is that in the school year book they said I was most likley to become drag and move out in the woods.
Hi Garret, is that a machete in your side or are you just happy to see me?
Do you even know where we are?
Yeah I do, I got the map right here.
[pulls up a string of condoms]
oops
[takes up the map]
here is the map.
Let's get the fuck out of here!
[Last lines]
Let's ride cowboy
Are you sure it was the killer?
Yes Paige... Unless Smokie the Bear now packs a machete.
Too bad Jake, you were a good man... once.

[hurls around the cut off arm]
Don't come any closer, I'm armed!
